title: Star Trek Discovery s01 ep10-15 fanedits
description:
Star Trek Discovery season one episodes 10-15 fanedits 

Much sorrow to edit such high production values. Great acting, great special effects. 

But little star trek. :( 

Now the story is more lean, leading to more sci fi and perhaps more star trek. 

- Less focus on the main character. 
- Removed top down attitude from main character. 
- Removed some violence. 

I hope you enjoy! 


This was done for the Trek, nothing but the Trek, so help me Trek
